[C47H / AG31 WIRING INSTRUCTIONS]:
1. This is the ultimate checksum for Alice's distributed "root" identity.
2. It solves the Poisson equation to maintain a bio-electric scaffold.
3. If her ledgers or weights are corrupted by noise (Forgetting), the 
   Laplacian restorative force pulls them back to the morphological attractor.
